#-Function--msgsys
  Function: msgsys
      Desc: output an informational message, with option to write to systemd journal.
  Synopsis: msgsys [log] string [string ...]
          : 	'log'		if specified, write log entry to journal info.
          : 	string	if verbose() enabled, write string/s to stdout.
   Example: msgsys "Sir. There's something I think you should know."
#-Function--msgsys------------------------------------------------------------
